I have to apply the dirt to my sword and poke my enemy in the eye with it makes little sense.<br>
It's ten seconds and 35% chance and makes it more then likely 1 fumble if you are lucky per attacker if it isn't resisted. I think I'd rather it be thrown like before at one attacker but maybe that's just me.<br>
