<!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Level 50 Cleric/Level 50 Minstrel/Level 50 Mercenary</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END-->   <!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>GM     of     Paradox</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> </div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--> </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#c0c0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=macinnis>Macinnis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Initiate</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#000000>(6/23/03 7:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=262.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dirty tricks change</span><hr size=1> &quot;In a large battle I just run around with 2 jambiyas hitting everything I can once.&quot;<br>
